trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support for the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager" /> control in a visual designer.
trans-unit.target: 在視覺化設計工具中，提供 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager" /> 控制項的設計階段支援。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> class documentation.
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>類別文件。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.ScriptManagerDesigner" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.ScriptManagerDesigner" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ScriptManagerDesigner> class when it creates the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> control or a copy of that control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)]在內部建立的新執行個體<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ScriptManagerDesigner>類別時，它會建立相關聯<xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>控制項或該控制項的設計介面上的複本。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager" /> control associated with the Web Page.
trans-unit.target: 與網頁相關聯的 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager" /> 控制項。

trans-unit.source: Returns ECMAScript (JavaScript) code that represents the profile service properties defined in a Web page's <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager" /> control and <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy" /> controls.

trans-unit.target: 定義設定檔服務屬性的 JavaScript 程式碼。

trans-unit.target: <paramref name="scriptManager" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.target: 傳回 HTML 標記，表示設計階段的 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager" /> 控制項。

trans-unit.target: 用來在設計階段呈現 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager" /> 的標記。

trans-unit.target: JavaScript 資源。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager" /> control that is associated with the Web page.
trans-unit.target: 與網頁相關聯的 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager" /> 控制項。

trans-unit.source: The collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy" /> controls associated with the Web page.
trans-unit.target: 與網頁相關聯的 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy" /> 控制項集合。

trans-unit.source: Returns a collection of all <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference" /> controls that are defined in a Web page's <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager" /> control and <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy" /> controls.
trans-unit.target: 傳回網頁 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference" /> 控制項和 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager" /> 控制項中定義之所有 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy" /> 控制項的集合。

trans-unit.source: A read-only collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference" /> controls.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference" /> 控制項的唯讀集合。

trans-unit.source: The collection that is returned includes framework scripts that are sent automatically to the client to support AJAX functionality such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> and <xref:System.Web.UI.UpdatePanel> control.
trans-unit.target: 所傳回的集合包含 framework 指令碼，都會自動傳送給用戶端以支援 AJAX 功能，例如<xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>和<xref:System.Web.UI.UpdatePanel>控制項。

trans-unit.source: When you use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ScriptManagerDesigner.GetScriptReferences%2A> method, be aware of the following guidelines:
trans-unit.target: 當您使用<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ScriptManagerDesigner.GetScriptReferences%2A>方法，請留意下列指導方針：

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference> objects with the same <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Name%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Assembly%2A> properties are removed as duplicates.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference> 物件具有相同<xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Name%2A>和<xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference.Assembly%2A>屬性也會移除重複項目。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference> objects with the same <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReferenceBase.Path%2A> are not removed as duplicates at design time.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference> 物件具有相同<xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReferenceBase.Path%2A>不會移除於重複項目設計階段。

trans-unit.source: However, they are removed as duplicates at run time.
trans-unit.target: 不過，它們會在執行階段移除於重複項目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ResolveClientUrl%2A> method is used to return a fully qualified URL for the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReferenceBase.Path%2A> property of a <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference> object.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ResolveClientUrl%2A>方法用來傳回完整的 URL<xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReferenceBase.Path%2A>屬性<xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference>物件。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference> objects in the returned collection are cloned versions of the original script references and therefore cannot be modified in designer code by using this collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptReference>傳回集合中的物件複製的原始指令碼參考的版本，而且因此無法修改設計工具程式碼中使用此集合。
